msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/legendre.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.legendre.legdiv:35
msgid ""
"In general, the (polynomial) division of one Legendre series by another "
"results in quotient and remainder terms that are not in the Legendre "
"polynomial basis set.  Thus, to express these results as a Legendre series, "
"it is necessary to \"reproject\" the results onto the Legendre basis set, "
"which may produce \"unintuitive\" (but correct) results; see Examples "
"section below."
msgstr ""

